<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %> | VKX Tech Documentation</title>
    <!-- Google Fonts: Inter -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg: #060B14;
            --accent: #38bdf8; /* Blue accent matching VKX style */
            --text-main: #FFFFFF;
            --text-muted: #94A3B8;
            --panel: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
            --border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
        }

        * { box-sizing: border-box; }

        body, html {
            margin: 0; padding: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;
            background-color: var(--bg);
            color: var(--text-main);
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, sans-serif;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        /* Abstract Glow background */
        .glow {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; bottom: 0;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at 50% -20%, rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.15) 0%, transparent 60%);
            z-index: 1;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .main-container {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 10;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 24px;
        }

        .header {
            position: absolute;
            top: 40px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
        }

        .logo-text {
            font-weight: 800;
            font-size: 20px;
            letter-spacing: -0.01em;
            color: var(--accent);
        }

        .card {
            background: var(--panel);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 24px;
            padding: 48px 32px;
            max-width: 540px;
            width: 100%;
            text-align: center;
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
        }

        .badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background: rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.1);
            color: var(--accent);
            padding: 6px 14px;
            border-radius: 100px;
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: 800;
            margin: 0 0 16px 0;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        }

        p {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .actions {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 12px;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 10px;
            padding: 18px 32px;
            border-radius: 14px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background-color: var(--accent);
            color: #000;
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px -5px rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.4);
        }

        .btn-outline {
            background-color: transparent;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            color: var(--text-main);
        }

        .btn-outline:hover {
            border-color: var(--accent);
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        }

        .footer-note {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 40px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            opacity: 0.5;
        }

        svg { width: 20px; height: 20px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="glow"></div>

    <div class="main-container">
        <header class="header">
            <div class="logo-text">VKX GROUP</div>
        </header>

        <div class="card">
            <div class="badge">Official Documentation</div>
            <h1><%= title %></h1>
            <p>Access our live documentation portal for real-time updates and interactive data.</p>
            
            <div class="actions">
                <a href="<%= notionUrl %>" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-primary">
                    Open Documentation Portal
                    <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14"></path></svg>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer-note">
            Secure documentation by VKX Tech Group. Verified for Institutional Grants.
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
